OL,3,CTrump says 'rigged election' means he
OL,4,Cgets to host World Cup and Olympics
OL,6,FDonald Trump said he gets to host the
OL,7,FWorld Cup and 2028 Olympics because
OL,8,F"they rigged the election".
OL,10,FThe president told a reception of the
OL,11,Finternational football governing body
OL,12,FFifa in New York he "was supposed to
OL,13,Fnot be here right now", in reference
OL,14,Fto the second and final four-year term
OL,15,Fhe would have served if he had won the
OL,16,F2020 election.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@ZO]tD@UOUuD@VO]
