CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784342915
OL,3,CTrump says 'rigged election' means he
OL,4,Cgets to host World Cup and Olympics
OL,6,FMr Trump's accusations of foreign
OL,7,Finterference and voter fraud come
OL,8,Fahead of crucial mid-term elections in
OL,9,FNovember, which could see Republicans
OL,10,Flose control of one or both houses of
OL,11,FCongress, leading critics to speculate
OL,12,Fhe is paving the way to challenge the
OL,13,Fresults.
OL,15,FDuring his first term in the White
OL,16,FHouse, the US secured both the 2026
OL,17,FWorld Cup, along with co-hosts Canada
OL,18,Fand Mexico, and the 2028 summer
OL,19,FOlympics, which will be staged in Los
OL,20,FAngeles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
