OL,3,CTrump says 'rigged election' means he
OL,4,Cgets to host World Cup and Olympics
OL,6,FSpeaking at the Fifa event at Trump
OL,7,FTower in Manhattan, Mr Trump said:
OL,8,F"All the way back in 2018, it was my
OL,9,Fhonour to help secure the World Cup
OL,10,Ffor North America, and never thinking
OL,11,Fthat it would turn out to be what it
OL,12,Fturned out to be.
OL,14,F"As fate would have it, I'm president.
OL,15,FI said, you know, I was supposed to
OL,16,Fnot be here right now.
OL,18,F"I was supposed to be president for
OL,19,Feight years, the polls showed it,
OL,20,Feveryone showed it.
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
