PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784342915
OL,3,CTrump says 'rigged election' means he
OL,4,Cgets to host World Cup and Olympics
OL,6,F"They rigged the election, and what
OL,7,Fdid I get? I got the World Cup, I got
OL,8,Fthe Olympics..."
OL,10,FReferring to the recent landmark
OL,11,Fanniversary of America's independence
OL,12,Ffrom Britain, the president added: "I
OL,13,Ftried to take credit for 250 years,
OL,14,Fbut that didn't work out as well."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@PO]tD@dOUvD@bO]
