OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784342915
OL,3,CTrump says 'rigged election' means he
OL,4,Cgets to host World Cup and Olympics
OL,6,FIn his speech, Mr Trump also made
OL,7,Freference to the controversial
OL,8,Foverturning of the ban given to US
OL,9,Fstriker Folarin Balogun following his
OL,10,Fred card against Bosnia, after he
OL,11,Fpersonally lobbied Fifa boss Gianni
OL,12,FInfantino.
OL,14,FThe decision, which enabled Balogun to
OL,15,Fplay in the team's knockout match
OL,16,Fagainst Belgium, sparked an
OL,17,Finternational backlash.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
