OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784342915
OL,3,CTrump says 'rigged election' means he
OL,4,Cgets to host World Cup and Olympics
OL,6,FMr Trump, who is to attend Sunday's
OL,7,Ffinal between Spain and Argentina,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This has been a tournament like
OL,9,Fno other, filled with fierce
OL,10,Fcompetition, unforgettable moments.
OL,12,F"Probably the most unforgettable is
OL,13,Fwhen they gave that gentleman, is it a
OL,14,Fred card? And I was forced to call
OL,15,FGianni and just make a recommendation."
OL,17,FHe recalled: "I said, 'I'd like to
OL,18,Fwage a complaint'. And actually, I
OL,19,Fdidn't. I had no idea what was going
OL,20,Fto happen.
OL,26,@pD@GOUtD@AOUwD@gO]yD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
