PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784342915
OL,3,CTrump says 'rigged election' means he
OL,4,Cgets to host World Cup and Olympics
OL,6,F"But you know, it's so much better the
OL,7,Fway it worked out because there's no
OL,8,Fcontroversy."
OL,10,FPointing to Belgium's 4-1 victory, Mr
OL,11,FTrump added: "They won the game, and
OL,12,Four team had all of its players."
OL,14,FHe told Infantino: "You made another
OL,15,Fgreat decision... I know you'll never
OL,16,Fget credit."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@MO]sD@NOUtD@aO]vD@TOUxD@LO]
