OL,3,CTrump says 'rigged election' means he
OL,4,Cgets to host World Cup and Olympics
OL,6,FElsewhere in his speech, Mr Trump also
OL,7,Fsuggested the US should be chosen
OL,8,Fagain to host the World Cup, but
OL,9,Fadded: "This time we'll leave Mexico
OL,10,Fand Canada out."
OL,12,FAnd highlighting the experience of
OL,13,Ffans, Mr Trump, whose mother is from
OL,14,FScotland, made special mention of the
OL,15,FTartan Army and how they "took over
OL,16,Fthe streets of Boston".
OL,18,FHe said: "A lot of countries came here
OL,19,Fnot knowing what to think, and they
OL,20,Flove the United States."
OL,26,@qD@HOUrD@PO]wD@ZOUxD@VO]zD@JOU|D@XO]
